<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TikTok Shop Project</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #e39cc2; 
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 10px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .image {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>About TikTok Shop</h1>
        <p>
            TikTok Shop is a new and innovative e-commerce platform integrated within the TikTok app. It allows businesses and creators to sell products directly through the platform, reaching a vast audience of TikTok users. By leveraging TikTok's engaging video content, TikTok Shop provides a unique shopping experience that blends social media and e-commerce seamlessly.
        </p>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="tiktok-shop-example.jpg" alt="TikTok Shop Example">
        </div>
        <p>
            TikTok Shop offers various features including live-stream shopping, in-app purchases, and promotional tools to help sellers maximize their reach and sales. With its easy-to-use interface and powerful marketing capabilities, TikTok Shop is poised to revolutionize the way people shop online.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
